languages.text: "Дурукарица. Повадки: подлость, злобность. Обитает: везде (прячется среди людей). Ест: не ест, питается богохульными мыслями. Боится: Императора, молитвы, праведных мыслей".
"Durrukhara. Behaviour: Villainy, malice. Habitat: Everywhere (hides among people). Diet: Doesn't eat, feeds on blasphemous thoughts. Fears: The Emperor, prayer, righteous thoughts."

languages.text: 「ドゥルカラ。挙動：邪悪、悪意に満ちている。生息地：あらゆる場所（人に擬態する）。食事：食べない。冒涜的な思考を食する。恐れるもの：皇帝、祈り、正義の心」
languages.original_text: "Durrukhara. Behaviour: Villainy, malice. Habitat: Everywhere (hides among people). Diet: Doesn't eat, feeds on blasphemous thoughts. Fears: The Emperor, prayer, righteous thoughts."

languages.text: “褐暗林族。行为特征：穷凶极恶，狠毒成性。栖息地：到处都是（隐藏在人群之中）。食性：不吃东西，只以亵渎的思想为食。弱点：帝皇，祈祷，正义的思想。”
languages.original_text: "Durrukhara. Behaviour: Villainy, malice. Habitat: Everywhere (hides among people). Diet: Doesn't eat, feeds on blasphemous thoughts. Fears: The Emperor, prayer, righteous thoughts."

languages.text: «Durrukhara. Comportamiento: Villanía, maldad. Hábitat: Cualquier parte (se esconden entre nosotros). Dieta: No necesita comer, se alimenta de ideas blasfemas. Miedos: El Emperador, la oración, pensamientos rectos».

languages.text: « Durrukhara. Comportement : infamie, malveillance. Habitat : partout (se dissimule parmi les humains). Régime alimentaire : se nourrit exclusivement de pensées blasphématoires. Faiblesses : l'Empereur, la prière, les pensées vertueuses. »
languages.original_text: "Durrukhara. Behaviour: Villainy, malice. Habitat: Everywhere (hides among people). Diet: Doesn't eat, feeds on blasphemous thoughts. Fears: The Emperor, prayer, righteous thoughts."

languages.text: "Durrukhara. Verhalten: bösartig, hinterhältig. Vorkommen: überall (versteckt sich unter Menschen). Ernährung: frisst nicht, lebt von blasphemischen Gedanken. Ängste: der Imperator, Gebete, rechtschaffene Gedanken."

languages.text: "Durrukhara. Davranış biçimi: Hainlik, kötülük. Habitat: Her yer (insanlar arasında gizlenir). Beslenme: Gıda almaz, kâfirce düşüncelerden beslenir. Korkular: İmparator, dua, doğru düşünceler."
